Text:
@Jared Leto: It probably isn't you posting, but if it is, you should know that I am also aware of this travesty. 

That's why I say, FOR GREAT ARTISTS, DONATE MONEY DIRECTLY TO THEM TO SHOW YOUR SUPPORT!!! BUT DO NOT BUY THE CD!!! Fuck the music industry execs. 

You should owe them nothing, Jared. My life would not be the same without you and your music.
